!!!EED: Ève Poudrier
!!!EEV: 2026/04/22
!!!RNB: Gagnon identifies two versions depending on whether a man or a woman are at the center of the dance; the version ended here is the man's version. Each version also has two variants based on whether or not the potential danse partner accepts or not the invitation of the speaker (see: "Ou bien, si la danseuse n'est pas agréée:"). Both these variants are encoded. Variant 1 comprises v:1-4 and variant 2 replaces v:4 and adds v:5-6.
